race.comment: QUICK BUCK (2) back in trip and another win looks imminent. Stalked the speed but failed to close off late with the 60kg when an even third over 2370m at Grafton. Kept fresh and has a key jockey change today. Nicely placed to give this a mighty shake. HIGHLAND HUSTLE (7) starting to hit her straps and confident she will get the 2000m this prep. Three weeks between runs when a tenacious on speed nose second over 1812m at this track. At her top and gets every chance to run this out. YAMBA'S GIRL (6) massive drop in grade when a fighting second over the 1600m at Taree. Can get cover from the draw and stake her claim. FULMEN FILOU (3) consistent stayer who resumed over the unsuitable trip with a sound second over 1600m at Moree. Regular rider back on and finds a winnable race.
